<br>
Point blank, you are a monk. You can level to 60 naked with just your damn fists (it'd take a lot longer, but it CAN technically be done).<br>
<br>
Your gear is fine. You can level, have fun, group, have fun, and play and have fun with that gear setup. Upgrades will come, plat will come. Don't pressure yourself too much to reach some sort of &quot;standard.&quot;<br>
<br>
But also, do set goals and do try and achieve them.<br>
<br>
If that makes any sense.<br>
<br>
In any event, you're right spore covered drops are a LOT rarer these days. Kinda sucks, since Polished Steel Ulak drops are insanely common these days. VI's tinkering with the already messed up Luclin loot tables has really just been one stupid decision after another. WOOT! Go GO PATCH TEAM!<br>
<br>
